##  Arch Linux Packge Info
## -------------------------

# explicitly installed Packges [I installed them by typing command]
pacman -Qe >> package_info/explicitly_installed

# Yay Packages [User Repos]
pacman -Qm >> package_info/yay_installed

# Pacman Packages [Official]
pacman -Qn >> package_info/pacman_installed

# Packages That a orphan [Not needed By any other Package]
pacman -Qt >> package_info/Not_needed_by_others

# All Packages Installed 
pacman -Q >> package_info/All_Packages
